22 program only to the extent the organization has secured one dollar of matching funds from
23 nonstate sources for every two dollars provided by the state historical society.
24 SECTION 7. OTHER FUNDS - BANK OF NORTH DAKOTA LINE OF CREDIT - MILITARY
25 GALLERY EXPANSION PROJECT. The other funds line item in section 1 of this Act includes
26 the sum of $20,000,000, which the state historical society may borrow through a line of credit
27 from the Bank of North Dakota during the biennium beginning July 1, 2025, and ending
28 June 30, 2027. The interest rate on the line of credit may not exceed the prevailing interest rate
29 charged to North Dakota governmental entities. If the state historical society accesses the line
30 of credit, the state historical society shall request a deficiency appropriation from the seventieth
31 legislative assembly to repay the line of credit.
